      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·大雅·生民之什·003.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">既醉.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>既醉以酒，爾殽既將。君子萬年，介爾昭明。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>You have made us drink to the full of your spirits;
Your viands were set out before us.
May you enjoy, O our lord, myriads of years!
May your bright intelligence ever be increased!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__daya-shengmin-003__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
