      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·大雅·生民之什·003.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">既醉.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>昭明有融，高朗令終。令終有俶，公尸嘉告。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>May your bright intelligence become perfect,
High and brilliant, leading to a good end!
That good end has (now) its beginning:—
The
personators of your ancestors announced it in their blessing.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__daya-shengmin-003__004__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
