      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·大雅·生民之什·003.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">既醉.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>其告維何？籩豆靜嘉。朋友攸攝，攝以威儀。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>What was their announcement?
'(The offerings) in your dishes of bamboo and wood are clean and
​fine.
Your friends, assisting in the service,
Have done their part with reverent demeanour.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__daya-shengmin-003__005__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
