      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·大雅·生民之什·003.6</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">既醉.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>其類維何？室家之壼。君子萬年，永錫祚胤。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>What will the blessings be?
'That along the passages of your palace,
You shall move for ten thousand years,
And there will be granted to you for ever dignity and posterity.'</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__daya-shengmin-003__007__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
