      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·大雅·生民之什·003.8</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">既醉.8</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>其僕維何？釐爾女士。釐爾女士，從以孫子。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>How is it attached?
'There is given you a heroic wife.
There is given you a heroic wife,
And from her shall come the (line of) descendants.'</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
